Rating: 1
I like swiss chard and stuffing, but do not like this combination. I made the recipe exactly and served with Turkey. The swiss chard I used was of good quality and fairly mild when I tasted raw, but it is too strong for the stuffing. Perhaps, too much in recipe I don't know. If you do make this, suggest you serve w/a more robust meat such as lamb or beef.

