have made it twice, quite tasty and guests raved about it. swapped in extra celery for the chard the 2nd time and it was still fabulous.

Rating: 4
I've made this twice now and it's turned out awesome. I 3 me some stuffing, but this is stuffing with an extra side of veggies which is just fabulous. As you can see, the recipe calls for chard, but I used kale once instead and that worked out fine. I think and equivalent portion of any green like spinach or whatever is cheap will also work! Also, go ahead and double the amount of fresh herbs in the recipe... you have to buy that whole package of them in the store anyhow and the stuffing really benefits from it!